Package team19.weatherapp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    App is the main class that will be loaded.
    AppTest
    Unit test for simple App.
    City
    City class holds the information for the three city properties: Current Weather Short Term Forecast Long Term Forecast The city object encapsulates these three objects, and allows the user to access all of the city data through one object.
    CurrentWeather
    The CurrrentWeather class holds all of the current weather data for the specified city.
    ErrorHandler
    The ErrorHandler class contains any special error handling methods that will be required for our objects.
    JSONRetriever
    The JSONRetriever class handles the process of retrieving and converting the openweathermap data.
    Location
    The Location class allows us to look up specific location from a data set.
    LongTermForecast
    The LongTermForecast class holds all of the long term weather data for the specified city.
    MainFrame
    The MainFrame class is the JFrame that holds the GUI.
    MainPanel
    The MainPanel class handles the GUI and user interface functionality of the program.
    MyLocations
    The MyLocations class is where user locations are saved.
    Serialize
    The Serialize class saves user data into a serialized file.
    Settings
    The Settings class allows the program to easily set global variables such as temperature, speed, etc.
    ShortTermForecast
    The ShortTermForecast class holds all of the long term weather data for the specified city.
    Utilities
    The Utilities class contains methods that allow us to convert between units.
